This is a log of applying pari(poly).hyperellratpoints to Pieza's pairs.

The idea is to choose u and build a formula in v for t^2 like Fulea does in 
https://mathoverflow.net/questions/463780/a-parametric-elliptic-curve-for-x4y4z4-1
Then apply pari(poly).hyperellratpoints to find candidate v for
Pieza's pairs method of finding new solutions to the Fermat quartic.

